<ext_description linkend="Description_assignment_arm.Description_text">
A <b>Description_text</b> is a set of words that describe something.
<example>The same thing may have multiple descriptions associated with it. Relating both a short description and
a long description to an operational activity or an organization, as required by the US DoD Architecture Framework, are examples of multiple descriptions applied to the same item.</example>
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Description_assignment_arm.Description_text.description">
the text that constitutes the description
</ext_description>

<ext_description linkend="Description_assignment_arm.Description_text_assignment">
A <b>Description_text_assignment</b> is the assignment of a description to something.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Description_assignment_arm.Description_text_assignment.description">
the text that constitutes the description
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Description_assignment_arm.Description_text_assignment.items">
the set of items being described
</ext_description>
